{"tid":495344,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"重睇犬夜叉完結篇 長文慎入","createTime":"2017-12-10T15:28:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T17:14:30.000Z","uid":153790,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"89bd32212db80021462402c2fda24b58f1396558","tid":495344,"uid":153790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T15:28:36.000Z","msg":"重睇完覺得殺生丸真係好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想做佢身邊既小玲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算係邪見都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比我跟佢一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好中意高冷型 但溫柔體貼識諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n犬夜叉都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為愛既人博命都要保護佢<br />\n呀籬同吉梗都好幸福<br />\n雖然佢地係同一個人<br />\n前世與今生<br />\n但係好大分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔可以將佢地視作同一個人<br />\n見到呀籬最後同犬夜叉邁向明天...<br />\n好撚幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過呀籬係人類 好快死<br />\n淨番犬夜叉一個so sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得奈落好可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來個願望只係想得到結梗既愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真心on999 好似毒撚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要傷害咁多人 犧牲哂自己既分身<br />\n明明佢d分身都好為佢賣命<br />\n神樂神無個堆 佢都可以咁賤殺佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你地有咩感想？？大家分享下"},{"pid":"df38225b83f4ccd797fdd039778d09a359ae4a41","tid":495344,"uid":82404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T15:36:34.000Z","msg":"爆碎牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee79827453fc50023499fe5592e457bfe0571724","tid":495344,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0