f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為殺生丸趕黎睇佢...<br />\n仲諗住用天生牙救佢<br />\n可惜遲左步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ec5dcbe9b6cc00091bbde196293b3aa7204376","tid":495344,"uid":153790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T09:08:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日翻睇文化祭舞台劇\u001d果集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n同埋有兩個蘿莉巫女果集 好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個集好正 好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n犬夜叉一黎到現代有危險就有鐵碎牙<br />\n完結篇有集用刀殺曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑撚死左"},{"pid":"b94448c4adcdfe9261286f6b6f5380ff88a51985","tid":495344,"uid":153790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T09:10:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個陣好鍾意睇犬夜叉去現代d劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n桔梗死個場面唯美到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對！我都中意睇佢去現代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個反差好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結梗死個陣可以係最愛既人懷抱中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜都值得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae73c6b566a8757eab08fb69851e965326d99c2","tid":495344,"uid":32606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T09:10:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>阿籬冇得返去現世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咩？作者無交帶有無得番....<br />\n只係話呀籬揀左戰國時代生活...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果無得番現代<img src